import os

def list_suids(path):
    suids = []
    for root, dirs, files in os.walk(path):
        for f in files:
            filepath = os.path.join(root, f)
            mode = os.stat(filepath).st_mode
            if mode & 0o4000:
                suids.append(filepath)
